frames.caption: A surreal scene where a painting of a river and mountains appears to come to life, with water flowing out of the frame and onto the living room floor. A ship sails from the painting into the room, creating a fantastical blend of art and reality.
frames.description: The image depicts a living room with a painting on the wall that seems to merge with reality. Water flows from the painting, creating a river on the floor, and a ship sails out of the painting, blurring the lines between the artwork and the physical space.

frames.caption: A surreal scene where a painting of a serene lake and mountains appears to come to life, with water flowing out of the frame into the room. A small boat is seen navigating the water that spills onto the wooden floor, creating a fantastical blend of art and reality.
frames.description: The image depicts a living room with a painting on the wall that has come to life. The painting shows a lake surrounded by mountains, and the water from the painting flows out into the room, where a small boat is sailing on it.

frames.caption: A surreal scene where a painting of a serene lake and mountains appears to overflow, with water cascading out of the frame and onto the floor. The water flows between two sofas, creating a striking contrast between the natural and indoor elements.
frames.description: The image depicts a living room with a painting that seems to come to life, as water from the depicted lake flows out into the room. This creates an imaginative blend of art and reality, transforming the space into a dreamlike environment.
